      "comment" : {
        "undefined" : "Both denote the generic notion of a product. DPPO’s Product is defined as the thing a DPP describes; CEON’s Product aligns with the same ISO definition. Thus, a one-to-one equivalence is appropriate, enabling a DPP-described product instance to be recognized as a CEON product instance."
      },
